TITLE: Initializing and Using Dexie.js in HTML Example
DESCRIPTION: Basic example showing how to initialize a Dexie database, define a schema, add data, and query it in a vanilla HTML page using script tags. Demonstrates database creation, schema versioning, and basic CRUD operations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dexie/Dexie.js/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: html
