TITLE: Implementing Basic Import Function in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates a simple import function for Dexie.js databases. It clears existing data and bulk adds new rows for each table in a transaction.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dexie/Dexie.js/blob/master/addons/dexie-export-import/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function import(data, db) {
    return db.transaction('rw', db.tables, () => {
        return Promise.all(data.map (t =>
            db.table(t.table).clear()
              .then(()=>db.table(t.table).bulkAdd(t.rows)));
    });
}
```

