TITLE: Exporting Non-Dexie IndexedDB Databases
DESCRIPTION: Example of how to export an IndexedDB database that wasn't created with Dexie and import it back, leveraging Dexie's ability to dynamically open existing databases.
SOURCE: https://github.com/dexie/Dexie.js/blob/master/addons/dexie-export-import/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import Dexie from 'dexie';
import 'dexie-export-import';

async function exportDatabase(databaseName) {
  const db = await new Dexie(databaseName).open();
  const blob = await db.export();
  return blob;
}

async function importDatabase(file) {
  const db = await Dexie.import(file);
  return db.backendDB();
}
```

